<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Thank you for getting an insurance quote from Kingsbridge.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Now you’ve reviewing your quotation documents,<b>&nbsp;is there anything you missed?</b><br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Here are the types of coverage you can add to your policy:</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"></p><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Cyber Liability</b>&nbsp;- Covers your business from risks related to your&nbsp;<b>technology and IT infrastructure.</b></font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>IR35 Protect&nbsp;</b>- Protects limited company contractors from the potentially crippling costs that can follow an IR35 enquiry.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Legal Expenses</b>&nbsp;- Protects your business in the event of legal action.</font></li></ul><p></p><p style="font-size: 12pt;"></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If you&nbsp;<b>need to make a change to your quote</b>, reply with the best date and time for me to call you. Alternatively, you can give me a ring on<b>&nbsp;01242 808 740</b>.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Kind regards</span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: white;">,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>